sql_json.natural_language: Summarize the last 3 messages on the most recent thread.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE threadId = (SELECT threadId FROM email_search_index ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 3;

sdk_json.from_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE threadId = (SELECT threadId FROM email_search_index ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 3;
sdk_json.translated_sdk_code:
latest_thread = db.collection('email_search_index').order_by('sentAt', direction=firestore.Query.DESCENDING).limit(1).get()
if latest_thread:
    thread_id = latest_thread[0].get('threadId')
    messages = db.collection('email_search_index').where('threadId', '==', thread_id).order_by('sentAt', direction=firestore.Query.DESCENDING).limit(3).get()
